          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Mini Game - Lords of Lunar -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Insert the Making of Lunar CD and when the video starts press Up, Down, Left, Right, Triangle, Start.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Rememberizer -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">To get the rememberizer, after you've become Dragonmaster, but before going to the Frontier, visit Ramus' shop and keep talking to him for a few times and he will give it to you. With this you can view the FMV scenes which you've already seen in the game so far.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; View All FMV Scenes -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After entering the hidden game code, open the Playstation and replace the ''Making of lunar'' CD with either of the 2 game discs. Now select ''Exit'' you will see all the movie scenes on that disc.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite Money  -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801DC37C E0FF<br>801DC37E 05F5</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Main character Infinite HP -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801DBFC0 03E7</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; 2nd character Infinite HP -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801DC100 03E7</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; 3rd character Infinite HP -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801DC240 03E7</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
